documents.name: Privacy Policy
documents.text:
Privacy Policy for all my Firefox, Chrome and Opera extensions

None of my browser extensions - I don't care about cookies, No, thanks, Restricted Mode: On, Youtube's Annotations No More or Autoplay No More - collects, uses or shares any personal or other kinds of data at all.

When reporting issues for I don't care about cookies and No, thanks extensions, your browser user agent will be anonymously sent by the report form for the debugging purposes.
